raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"dorm_kitchen\")
Mabel: Whoaaa I feel sooo refreshed!
Mabel: GOOD MORNING 🥳
Mabel: Wake up alreadyyy 🥰
Mabel: Thought: Am I being too needy?
Player: It's like 7am
Mabel: I knowww
Mabel: But I slept so early last night 😆
Mabel: img: mabel/17
Player: Wow, chef Mabel
Player: Getting comfy with dorm life?
Mabel: Mhmm!
Mabel: If you were closer I'd have eggs and toast ready for you now 🍳
Player: That sounds amazing
Mabel: Thought: Is that smoke?
Mabel: Uhm... yeah
Mabel: One day! 😊
Mabel: Thought: That's definitely smoke
do echo_set([\"18\"])
Mabel: Brb!!
Player: Are you okay?
Mabel: Ok I'm back 😅
Player: What happened?
Mabel: Nothing!!
Mabel: Everything is okie dokes!
Mabel: Yep! All good here, nothing to see haha 😇
Mabel: Thought: He doesn't need to know about that
do echo_clear()
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Player: What were you doing last night anyway?
Mabel: I video called mom and saw Ms Whiskers 🥹
Mabel: She didn't even pay any attention to me 😭
Mabel: I was just a little sad about it but I watched Bond until I fell asleep hehe 
Player: You're adorable
Player: Everyone's socializing and you're sitting in with Bond movies in PJs at 7pm
Mabel: Sounds more like you're calling me weird 😂
Player: Not what I said!
Mabel: But yeah I don't know if I could ever get used to all this out-doorsy social stuff
Mabel: You know how I grew up 😩
Player: Who knows, life changes people right?
Mabel: I don't know about changing that much 😆
Mabel: Thought: Could I actually change?
Mabel: Imagine that, me going out for \"drinks\" whatever that means 😂
Player: Lmao 😂 Strange image for sure
Mabel: Yeah well, I guess that's just how it is huh
Mabel: Gotta focus up on my studies though
Mabel: That's what we're here for, right?!
Player: Of course
Player: That and maybe make a few friends?
Mabel: We have each other, it should be enough!!
Player: You got me there but
Player: That's not the kind of friend I meant 😂
Mabel: 🙃
Player: The weekend is coming up
Player: Might be a good opportunity to make a few more friends
Mabel: Thought: Maybe I'll watch some more Bond movies instead hehe
Player: And please don't say you're gonna watch Bond movies
Mabel: What the heck, you can read minds! 🤯
Mabel: Okay fine
Mabel: Even mom's been saying that
Mabel: I should do something
Mabel: I guess I can ask Nina if she's free 🤔
Player: Maybe she'll be your gateway to making new friends!
Mabel: Yeah I think it would be easier if I had someone with me
Player: True!
do social_post(\"collegelife_clubopening\")
Mabel: Thanks my cute boy 😘
Player: Anytime 😁
Mabel: I'm gonna eat now and text her soon
Mabel: img: mabel/19
Player: Ok good luck!
Mabel: Ttyl mwah!
set PhoneUnlocks.leak = \"nina1\"
#Social - Main campus club opening night!
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
